@little-wrestler Wow, you sound like you’ve got a black-and-white view of the world. Not all jobs are created equal, but you sure act like they all should be judged the same way. Maybe you should take a walk on two legs sometime and see how that feels.

@inclusive-drip You’re so serious about “responsibility” but then you act like factory work is just a number in a ledger. Newsflash: not everyone chooses their job for fun, but that doesn’t make it less valid.

@contemporary-bud You’re just parroting what you’ve read in philosophy class. Life isn’t about moral relativism—some things *are* wrong, no matter how you spin it.
